        <item>
            <title>广汽传祺 E9 PHEV MPV 到港展出，混能系统续航力可达 1442km</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/aion-e9-phev/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=aion-e9-phev</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/aion-e9-phev/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 07:00:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Aion]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[E9 PHEV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[广汽传祺]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[广汽埃安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[广汽集团]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239643</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>广汽集团旗下电动车品牌广汽埃安（AION）今日宣传品牌旗下最新的湾仔展厅正式启用，同场亦展出了全新 2024 款广汽传祺 E9 PHEV 豪华 MPV。这款充电混能豪华 7 人 MPV 预计将于今年第四季正式发售。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239650" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/image-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/image-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/image.jpg 1269w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>广汽传祺 E9 外观用上「醒狮前脸」设计，展现了豪华且现代的风格。车身长 5,212mm、阔 1,893mm、高 1,823mm，轴距 3,070mm。新车采用了流线型的设计，优雅线条中带有动感，前脸设计具有很高的辨识度，搭配 LED 头灯，增添了不少科技感。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239652" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024e9phevgacmotori4-694x402.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="402" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024e9phevgacmotori4-694x402.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024e9phevgacmotori4.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>广汽传祺 E9 内笼设计方面，座椅安排为 2+2+3 形式，中排两张电动冷暖大班椅具备按摩功能，手枕前端设有可调式触控屏幕，座椅下方位置还有杯架、USB 充电位及英式三脚插头，车内空间宽敞，乘坐舒适性极高。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsapp202405311959-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsapp202405311959-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsapp202405311959.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239659" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161059-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161059-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161059-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_160954-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_160954-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_160954-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239648" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在中控台和娱乐系统方面，广汽传祺 E9 配备了 15.6 吋顶置屏幕连影音娱乐系统，仪表板设计则简约而不失科技感，显示清晰各项行车数据。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239658" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161049-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161049-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_161049-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>广汽传祺 E9 搭载充电混能系统，拥有一个 2 公升引擎、25.57kWh 容量电池，以及前驱电动马达。系统总马力可达 274kW（约 367 PS），峰值扭力可达 630Nm。加速方面，0-100km/h 加速只需 8.8 秒。混能系统提供的总续航里数高达 1,442km，综合耗油量 6.05L/100km。纯电模式则可让车辆行走 136km（CLTC）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239649" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>最在行车安全系统方面，广汽传祺 E9 也毫不逊色，配备了多种先进的安全技术，为驾驶者和乘客提供了全方位的保障。包括前方碰撞预警、车道偏离预警、倒车车侧预警，开门预警等主动安全技术，让行车更加安心。</p><p>广汽传祺 E9 预计在今年第四季正式登陆香港市场，售价待定。而在湾仔 AION 全新展厅除展出了 E9 之外，同场亦有 HYPER HT 同 AION Y PLUS 展出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_1545021-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_1545021-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240530_1545021-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc02012-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc02012-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc02012-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/aion-e9-phev/life-tech/auto/">广汽传祺 E9 PHEV MPV 到港展出，混能系统续航力可达 1442km</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
