        <item>
            <title>抖音接通公安打击网络暴力，禁滥用 AI 制图侮辱他人、泄露他人私隐、周围贴骂街评论</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/douyinchina/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=douyinchina</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/douyinchina/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 06:00:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[抖音]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239580</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>网络欺凌、网络骚扰问题，在资讯发达年代为不少人带来困扰。在 AI 流行后有更多受害者被 AI 绘图在网路上被公审。抖音宣布与公安机关建立线索回馈机制，将涉嫌违法犯罪的网暴线索即时报送至公安机关依法打击。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1239587 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024053174409-503x580.jpg" alt="" width="503" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024053174409-503x580.jpg 503w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024053174409.jpg 780w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 503px" /></p><p>中国抖音指今年至今处置 162 件网络暴力事件，拦截超过 5,000 万条评论，并警示近 70 万名施暴者。他们将推出「一键防网暴」功能，用户启用后，7 天内不会收到非选定人群发送的私信、弹幕及评论。若用户在平台内受到不当言论的伤害而不知如何用法律保护自己，抖音提供由中国法律咨询中心解答的法律咨询服务。抖音 App 防网暴功能入口：我 → 右上角菜单 → 更多功能 → 安全中心 → 小安防网暴 → 维权指引页面。</p><p>官方披露的四类典型违规行为包括：滥用 AI 技术对他人进行挖苦与侮辱、评论泄露他人私隐讯息、四处粘贴辱骂言论及频繁公开辱骂。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239582" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ff80cef4cdcb4d4d9273-249x580.jpg" alt="" width="249" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ff80cef4cdcb4d4d9273-249x580.jpg 249w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ff80cef4cdcb4d4d9273.jpg 386w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 249px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239583" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8a0d7ba916f2431b82e3-290x580.jpg" alt="" width="290" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8a0d7ba916f2431b82e3-290x580.jpg 290w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8a0d7ba916f2431b82e3.jpg 451w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 290px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239584" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/c86355f08da548439a72-354x580.jpg" alt="" width="354" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/c86355f08da548439a72-354x580.jpg 354w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/c86355f08da548439a72.jpg 549w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 354px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239585" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6ed72c7812d34e209a14-336x580.jpg" alt="" width="336" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6ed72c7812d34e209a14-336x580.jpg 336w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6ed72c7812d34e209a14.jpg 521w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 336px" /></p><div class="mceTemp"></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/772/235.htm">IT 之家</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/microsoft-cocreator/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】小画家也可 AI 生成图片　无须 VPN 免费用 Microsoft Cocreator</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/23/tinamind/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】AI 中文总结外语网页、YouTube 影片，免 VPN 免费 ChatGPT 网页工具  </a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/23/superclue-sensechatv5/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国 AI 击败 GPT-4 成榜首，多项能力评测表现最好</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/01/douyinchina/life-tech/social-network/">抖音接通公安打击网络暴力，禁滥用 AI 制图侮辱他人、泄露他人私隐、周围贴骂街评论</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
